    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. While it runs well and has been maintained mechanically, the exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and a few minor dings along the passenger side. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing function and value over a perfect finish.",
