    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for the driver who prioritizes both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This automobile exhibits a well-preserved exterior and a refined interior, reflecting a history of diligent care and consistent servicing. Rigorously inspected to ensure peak operational performance, it offers a balanced driving experience that remains both responsive and composed. This is a distinguished opportunity to acquire a vehicle of proven integrity and enduring value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
